# Real Estate Lead Assistant

## Project Overview
A backend application built using FastAPI and SQLite to manage real estate customer leads.

## Features
- Add new leads
- View all leads
- Update lead status
- Search leads by name
- Filter leads by status

## Technologies Used
- Python
- FastAPI
- SQLite
- Swagger UI
- GitHub

## API Endpoints

### GET /
Checks if the API is running.

### POST /add-lead
Adds a new lead.

### GET /leads
Displays all leads.

### PUT /update-status/{lead_id}
Updates lead status.

### GET /search
Searches leads by name or status.

